{"tid":511913,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"加利佬問VVD抵唔抵買　加歷查串爆回應","createTime":"2017-12-28T02:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T05:55:21.000Z","uid":4661,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8d719dc9044d6dd80ee39777da85dedd34b7e4","tid":511913,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171228/large/1514426450_8632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171228%2Flarge%2F1514426450_8632.jpg&h=8df016a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171228/large/1514426451_34a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171228%2Flarge%2F1514426451_34a2.jpg&h=2b16f1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利物浦禮拜三晚失驚無神公佈1月1號就會正式喺修咸頓簽入後衛華基爾雲迪積克，呢位荷蘭國腳高達7,500萬鎊（約7.85億港元）嘅身價自然係各界嘅焦點。<br />\n<br />\nVVD就咁樣搖身變成全世界最貴嘅後衛，前曼聯右閘加利尼維利就喺Twitter tag咗加歷查，問佢覺得呢單交易抵唔抵。係人都知加利佬同加歷查踢波果陣勢成水火，兩個人退休之後一齊講波都經常擦出火花，估唔到加利佬問完無耐，隔咗唔夠20分鐘就收到加歷查嘅回覆，仲俾呢位前利物浦後衛搵到個靚位入咗紅魔鬼一嘢，順便抽水。<br />\n<br />\n到底加歷查點樣答加利佬嘅問題？<br />\n<br />\n「我都唔肯定，不過只係貴過域陀連迪路夫一倍嚟講，我覺得直頭係買得平喇！」域陀連迪路夫係邊個？咪係摩連奴今個夏天買返嚟，但擺多過踢、只係喺英超上陣八場嘅水貨瑞典後衛囉！"},{"pid":"a177d4bf1f3ac77c7d21858795e80ffa7fbb8276","tid":511913,"uid":132905,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:50:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c14c602429b689a2b7cfda4de2682719c6496df","tid":511913,"uid":19660,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"佢2個fd過打band啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc95bcb26f279be6885a533709dd2040829ed61","tid":511913,"uid":51076,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"連迪路夫呢幾場都開始唔錯，應該都有潛質"},{"pid":"344112f76652062cdcf152e7c1603e233db68557","tid":511913,"uid":1984,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"白LIN好似無想像中咁水"},{"pid":"ae07e11937880453922ea3e0240385339f4c4f71","tid":511913,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"費蘭尼，伊巴呢d又係擺多過踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但人工講緊係170000以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67466455ad8e7f0fabe15c986dbf86285949afd4","tid":511913,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"連迪路夫唔渣啦屌"},{"pid":"5168f8a0926f61330deb8560836972ae4445bba4","tid":511913,"uid":6548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ae07e11937880453922ea3e0240385339f4c4f71","tid":511913,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"費蘭尼，伊巴呢d又係擺多過踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但人工講緊係170000以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:08:24.000Z","msg":"c朗筆錢未用完同廢老賣球衫夠晒"},{"pid":"8a5848cc7901e16c4fda9183395c519b1237a511","tid":511913,"uid":26708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae07e11937880453922ea3e0240385339f4c4f71","tid":511913,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"費蘭尼，伊巴呢d又係擺多過踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但人工講緊係170000以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T03:09:50.000Z","msg":"Fellaini  戰術岩 就幾勁<br />\nIbra 就算啦"},{"pid":"5d93ee1c760bfb7b406f83dcd47b293ecfe5a066","tid":511913,"uid":872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae07e11937880453922ea3e0240385339f4c4f71","ti